2002-1654 (La. 10/14/02)

Jerri Page DUBOIS v. Kevin W. BROWN; Tim Gilmore; American Motorists Insurance Company; and Farm Bureau Insurance Company. No. 2002-C-1654. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 14, 2002.

In re Farm Bureau Insurance Company; — Defendant; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review, Parish of E. Baton Rouge, 19th Judicial District Court *422Div. N, No. 435,981; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, No. 2001-CA-0816.

Denied.

VICTORY, J., would grant the writ. TRAYLOR, J., would grant the writ. KNOLL, J., would grant the writ.
